org.wildfly.swarm.config.security

Class SecurityDomain<T extends SecurityDomain<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap
        • org.wildfly.swarm.config.security.SecurityDomain<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map

    public class SecurityDomain<T extends SecurityDomain<T>>
extends HashMap
    Configures a security domain. Authentication, authorization, ACL, mapping, auditing and identity trust are configured here.

      • cacheType

        public SecurityDomain.CacheType cacheType()
        Adds a cache to speed up authentication checks. Allowed values are 'default' to use simple map as the cache and 'infinispan' to use an Infinispan cache.

      • cacheType

        public T cacheType(SecurityDomain.CacheType value)
        Adds a cache to speed up authentication checks. Allowed values are 'default' to use simple map as the cache and 'infinispan' to use an Infinispan cache.
